    <abstract id="aspace_6ee0d051152b262fa4f970d930807a15" label="Abstract">Jerome Allen was a professor and dean at New York University's School of Pedogogy. This collection comprises a selection of his published writings, including essays, books, and lectures, from the years 1867-1893.</abstract>
